<record_update table="sys_report">
    <sys_report action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE">
        <aggregate>COUNT</aggregate>
        <aggregation_source/>
        <chart_size>medium</chart_size>
        <description>Manager View dashboard donut/pie widget data source. Aggregates ALL records in x_[scope]_case grouped by the type Choice field with COUNT(*) per bucket. Two slices expected (General Inquiry, Complaint) when seed data spans both case types; the type field is extensible per AAP Section 0.5.7 so future Choice additions automatically appear as new slices without report modification. UNFILTERED by design - shows the entire team caseload split between the two case-handling pipelines (one Flow Designer flow per case type), enabling managers to assess subdomain volume balance and pipeline-staffing needs. Replaces ArkCase's CaseFile.caseType + Pentaho aggregation pipeline with a native GlideAggregate-backed sys_report. Different aggregation than x_[scope]_all_cases_by_status (group by status) and x_[scope]_all_cases_by_priority (group by priority); same dashboard audience per AAP Section 0.4.4.</description>
